creator: Health Promotion Board
descriptionHtml:
One-stop access to health records of your family, friends, children. Learn, manage and improve your health, schedule your appointments, check your personal health records, access your immunisation, screening and lab test results, view your child’s upcoming immunisation schedule and more*!

HealthHub is your personal digital health companion by the Ministry of Health and Health Promotion Board Singapore.

Features:

• Appointments: Make, view, reschedule, cancel
• Medications: Access your prescription records and medication lists
• Refill: Request for medication refill or renewal of prescription
• Payments: Pay for your medical bills
• Admissions (Financial Counselling): View your estimated cost, change ward type, make online payment for deposit
• Children Health: Track your child’s developmental milestones and vaccination records as well as upcoming immunisation schedule
• Family Health: View your parents’ medical appointments and medication lists
• School Health: Get notified of school health assessments and your child’s referral letters
• Directory Listing: Find doctors, caregivers, 24 hour CHAS clinics easily
• Healthpoints: Be rewarded when you complete quizzes

* Participating restructured hospitals, polyclinics and specialist outpatient clinics from the public healthcare sector.
descriptionShort: The ultimate health app for Singaporeans. Medical records, health info, rewards.

title: HealthHub SG

creator: Integrated Health Information Systems Pte Ltd
descriptionHtml:
HealthHub’s nation-wide suite of digital health services and personalised advice lets you seamlessly care for yourself and those you love.

With the HealthHub app, you can manage appointments, bills and payments across public healthcare institutions* and access your personal health records or that of your loved ones including COVID-19 vaccination records and laboratory test results.

Useful Features:

Appointments: View, book, reschedule, cancel your medical appointments
Queue Number: Retrieve your queue number from the app
Covid-19 records: View your vaccination records and test results
Lab Tests: View your laboratory test results
Medications: Access your prescription records and request for refill
Payment: Pay for your medical bills across hospitals
Adult Immunisation: Check your immunisation records and eligibility for subsidies
My Health Booklet: Check your eligibility for subsidised screening programmes
Children Health: Track your child’s developmental milestones and immunisation records as well as upcoming immunisation schedule
Family Health: View your parents’ medical appointments, medication lists and more

* Participating restructured hospitals, polyclinics and specialist outpatient clinics from the public healthcare sector.

title: HealthHub SG

creator: Integrated Health Information Systems Pte Ltd
descriptionHtml:
HealthHub SG is a national digital healthcare platform that allows you to conveniently manage you and your loved ones’ health in one place.

Access your health records as well as perform various transactions across public healthcare institutions* such as appointment booking, bill payment and medication refill with the HealthHub app.


Quick Access:

Conveniently access selected health records and e-Services using your mobile biometrics or 6-digit passcode.


Quick Links:

Locate and browse popular e-Services easily.


Appointment and Mobile Registration:
Manage your medical appointments centrally, as well as pre-register to obtain a queue number prior to your appointment.


Payment:

Retrieve past invoices and make payments for current medical bills digitally.


Health Profile and Caregiver Access:
Enable caregiver access to view health records and perform digital healthcare transaction for yourself as well as your child, dependent(s) or loved ones.


* Participating restructured hospitals, polyclinics and specialist outpatient clinics from the public healthcare sector.
descriptionShort: Manage your public healthcare transactions and records conveniently with one app

Access your health records as well as perform various transactions across public healthcare institutions* such as appointment booking, bill payment and medication refill with the HealthHub app.


Quick Access:

Conveniently access selected health records and e-Services using your mobile biometrics or 6-digit passcode.


Quick Links:

Locate and browse popular e-Services easily.


Appointment and Mobile Registration:
Manage your medical appointments centrally, as well as pre-register to obtain a queue number prior to your appointment.


Payment:

Retrieve past invoices and make payments for current medical bills digitally.


Health Profile and Caregiver Access:
Enable caregiver access to view health records and perform digital healthcare transaction for yourself as well as your child, dependent(s) or loved ones.


* Participating restructured hospitals, polyclinics and specialist outpatient clinics from the public healthcare sector.
descriptionShort: Manage your public healthcare transactions and records conveniently with one app

appDetails.developerName: Synapxe Pte Ltd
appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Enjoy an improved experience in managing your health records and transactions with HealthHub’s latest updates and fixes.
- In the Health Profile page, you can scroll horizontally to locate all e-Services at a glance.
